  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pets Walks Around Your Taskbar</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute pets live at the bottom of your screen while you do other things.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549370/extras/e7adea6ddd748f1d602719087705b5ef.poster.avif?t=1772316240\" width=800 height=95 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549370/extras/e7adea6ddd748f1d602719087705b5ef.webm?t=1772316240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pet Your Pets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget the love your pets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549370/extras/863ab4dc79f2725743d1bb75be405d72.poster.avif?t=1772316240\" width=800 height=325 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549370/extras/863ab4dc79f2725743d1bb75be405d72.webm?t=1772316240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pets Menu</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You Can See Your All Pets On The Pets Menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549370/extras/7afdfd776b3d99f4bbd145f7fa3ef88b.poster.avif?t=1772316240\" width=522 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549370/extras/7afdfd776b3d99f4bbd145f7fa3ef88b.webm?t=1772316240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Throw And Catch Your Pets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play with your pets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549370/extras/b8c244046ad31f19097ae0ade1dc580a.poster.avif?t=1772316240\" width=800 height=769 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549370/extras/b8c244046ad31f19097ae0ade1dc580a.webm?t=1772316240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You Can Size Your Pets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can make them huge and tiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549370/extras/ccaec60c4e8a7dcce99c0c7951b34d34.poster.avif?t=1772316240\" width=800 height=757 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549370/extras/ccaec60c4e8a7dcce99c0c7951b34d34.webm?t=1772316240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pets Walks Around Your Taskbar</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute pets live at the bottom of your screen while you do other things.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549370/extras/e7adea6ddd748f1d602719087705b5ef.poster.avif?t=1772316240\" width=800 height=95 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549370/extras/e7adea6ddd748f1d602719087705b5ef.webm?t=1772316240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pet Your Pets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget the love your pets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549370/extras/863ab4dc79f2725743d1bb75be405d72.poster.avif?t=1772316240\" width=800 height=325 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549370/extras/863ab4dc79f2725743d1bb75be405d72.webm?t=1772316240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pets Menu</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You Can See Your All Pets On The Pets Menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549370/extras/7afdfd776b3d99f4bbd145f7fa3ef88b.poster.avif?t=1772316240\" width=522 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3549370/extras/7afdfd776b3d99f4bbd145f7fa3ef88